console 下交换键位
1.复制/usr/share/keymaps/i386/qwerty/us.map.gz 到lyt.map.gz
2.解压lyt.map.gz,修改其中的Caps_lock 和 Control对应的keycodes
3.压缩lyt.map 
4.修改/etc/vconsole.conf 改为KEYMAP=lyt

X 下交换键位
添加以下内容到/etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/00-keyboard.conf
# Read and parsed by systemd-localed. It's probably wise not to edit this file
# manually too freely.
Section "InputClass"
	Identifier "system-keyboard"
	MatchIsKeyboard "on"
	Option "XkbLayout" "us"
	Option "XkbOptions" "ctrl:swapcaps"
EndSection


然后reboot
